@using SimeSoft.Components.State
@inject PagoState PagoState
<aside class="sidebar @(MenuAbierto ? "" : "cerrado")">

    <div class="brand">
        <div class="brand-logo">
            <img src="/img/logo.png" />
        </div>

        <h2>SIME</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="line"></div>

    <nav class="menu">
        

        <NavLink href="/matricula/inicio" class="menu-item" @onclick="LimpiarPagos">
            <i class="bi bi-house-door-fill"></i>
            <span>Inicio</span>
        </NavLink>

        <NavLink href="/matricula/matriculas"
                 class="menu-item"
                 Match="NavLinkMatch.All">
            <i class="bi bi-person-fill-add"></i>
            <span>Matrículas</span>
        </NavLink>

        <NavLink href="/matricula/matriculas/historial"
                 class="menu-item"
                 Match="NavLinkMatch.Prefix">
            <i class="bi bi-clock-history"></i>
            <span>Historial</span>
        </NavLink>

        <NavLink href="/matricula/pagos" class="menu-item">
            <i class="bi bi-cash-stack"></i>
            <span>Pagos</span>
        </NavLink>

        <NavLink href="/matricula/personal" class="menu-item" @onclick="LimpiarPagos">
            <i class="bi bi-people-fill"></i>
            <span>Personal</span>
        </NavLink>

        <NavLink href="/matricula/aulas" class="menu-item">
            <i class="bi bi-display"></i>
            <span>Aulas</span>
        </NavLink>

        <NavLink href="/matricula/alumnos" class="menu-item" @onclick="LimpiarPagos">
            <i class="bi bi-mortarboard-fill"></i>
            <span>Alumnos</span>
        </NavLink>

    </nav>

    <div class="logout-section">
        <div class="line"></div>

        <NavLink href="/login" class="menu-item logout">
            <i class="bi bi-box-arrow-right"></i>
            <span>Cerrar sesión</span>
        </NavLink>
    </div>

</aside>

<style>
    .sidebar {
        width: 285px;
        min-width: 285px;
        min-height: 100vh;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #06164a, #294878);
        color: white;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        padding: 18px 14px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        overflow: hidden;
    }

        .sidebar.cerrado {
            width: 0;
            min-width: 0;
            padding-left: 0;
            padding-right: 0;
        }

            .sidebar.cerrado * {
                opacity: 0;
                pointer-events: none;
            }

    .brand {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 14px;
        padding: 4px 6px;
        white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .brand-logo {
        width: 68px;
        height: 68px;
        background: transparent;
        border-radius: 12px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 6px;
    }

        .brand-logo img {
            width: 58px;
            height: 58px;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

    .brand h2 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 32px;
        font-weight: 900;
        line-height: 1;
    }

        

    .line {
        height: 2px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
        border-radius: 20px;
        margin: 18px 0 22px 0;
    }

    .menu {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 14px;
    }

    .menu-item {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 18px;
        padding: 15px 16px;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 14px;
        font-size: 21px;
        font-weight: 800;
        transition: all 0.25s ease;
        white-space: nowrap;
    }

        .menu-item i {
            font-size: 30px;
            width: 34px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .menu-item:hover {
            background: rgba(93, 159, 211, 0.75);
            color: white;
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }

        .menu-item.active {
            background: #315fa8;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.22);
        }

            .menu-item.active i {
                color: #ffd21f;
            }

    .logout-section {
        margin-top: auto;
    }

    .logout:hover {
        background: #d9534f;
    }
</style>

@code {
    [Parameter]
    public bool MenuAbierto { get; set; } = true;
    private void LimpiarPagos()
    {
        PagoState.LimpiarBusqueda();
    }
}